OL,3,CCampaigner backs Hillsborough Law
OL,4,C'legacy' after meeting with Keir
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FThe new Public Office (Accountability)
OL,8,FBill is intended to make sure the
OL,9,Fauthorities will face criminal
OL,10,Fsanctions if they attempt to cover up
OL,11,Fthe facts behind disasters such as the
OL,12,F1989 Hillsborough tragedy or the
OL,13,FGrenfell Tower fire.
OL,15,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer had
OL,16,Fpreviously pledged to bring in the law
OL,17,Fby the 36th anniversary of the
OL,18,Ftragedy, which was on April 15, but
OL,19,FDowning Street then said more time was
OL,20,Fneeded to redraft it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
