OL,4,C'legacy' after meeting with Keir
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,F"This is not just about a legacy for
OL,8,Fthe 97," she added, in reference to
OL,9,Fthe number of Liverpool fans who died
OL,10,Fin the tragedy.
OL,12,F"This is a legacy for the people of
OL,13,Fthis country and I think that is the
OL,14,Fmost important thing."
OL,16,FThe Prime Minister said the courage
OL,17,Fshown by the Hillsborough campaigners
OL,18,Fhad been "humbling".
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@HO]tD@AOUvD@VO]zD@JOUzD@SO]
