OL,4,C'legacy' after meeting with Keir
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FHe told them: "You have changed the
OL,8,Flives not just of the families
OL,9,Finvolved in all of those scandals and
OL,10,Finjustices, you are also going to
OL,11,Fchange the lives of thousands of
OL,12,Fpeople you will never meet, who for
OL,13,Fyears and years and decades and
OL,14,Fgenerations to come will now be able
OL,15,Fto point to what you have done and say
OL,16,F'we don't have to go through that'."
OL,18,FSome campaigners raised fears the
OL,19,FBill's contents had been diluted and
OL,20,Fwould not include a legal duty of
OL,21,Fcandour.
OL,26,@oD@OOUxD@dO]
