OL,4,C'legacy' after meeting with Keir
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FBut the Government has confirmed a new
OL,8,Fprofessional and legal duty of candour
OL,9,Fwill be part of the Bill, meaning
OL,10,Fpublic officials must act with honesty
OL,11,Fand integrity at all times and could
OL,12,Fface criminal sanctions if they breach
OL,13,Fit.
OL,15,FThe Hillsborough disaster led to the
OL,16,Fdeaths of 97 football fans during the
OL,17,FFA Cup semi-final between Liverpool
OL,18,Fand Nottingham Forest at the football
OL,19,Fground in Sheffield.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
