OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FThe Government said the new
OL,8,Flegislation will "end the culture of
OL,9,Fcover-ups" and learn lessons from
OL,10,Fwider disasters including the Grenfell
OL,11,FTower fire and the Post Office Horizon
OL,12,Fand infected blood scandals.
OL,14,FA spokesperson for the Hillsborough
OL,15,FLaw Now campaign warned the Bill must
OL,16,Fnot be weakened during its passage
OL,17,Fthrough Parliament and called on the
OL,18,FGovernment to "be brave and ignore the
OL,19,Fvested interests" of those who might
OL,20,Fattempt to water it down.
