OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV News after the
OL,8,Fmeeting, Ms Aspinall said she did not
OL,9,Fthink the Bill would be watered down.
OL,10,FShe joked: "I'll tell you what, it
OL,11,Fbetter not be because they'll have us
OL,12,Fto deal with again".
OL,14,F"I don't think they want to do that",
OL,15,Fshe added.
