OL,7,FMs Aspinall said she walked into
OL,8,FDowning Street "hopeful" this morning
OL,9,Fafter being greeted on the steps by
OL,10,Fthe Prime Minister. She said "he
OL,11,Fwhispered in my ear (and) I went in
OL,12,Fvery hopeful.
OL,14,F"I thought, yes, the Prime Minister's
OL,15,Fgot the message.
OL,17,F"He knows exactly where we stand and I
OL,18,Fknew he was going to do it - and he
OL,19,Fhas."
