OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FSir Keir said the new legislation can
OL,8,Fchange "the balance of power in
OL,9,FBritain" to ensure the state "can
OL,10,Fnever hide from the people it is
OL,11,Fsupposed to serve".
OL,13,FHe added: "Make no mistake, this a law
OL,14,Ffor the 97, but it is also a law for
OL,15,Fthe subpostmasters who suffered
OL,16,Fbecause of the Horizon scandal, the
OL,17,Fvictims of infected blood, and those
OL,18,Fwho died in the terrible Grenfell
OL,19,FTower fire. This is change only this
OL,20,FGovernment can deliver."
OL,26,@pD@HOUqD@HO]qD@^OUsD@RO]uD@KOU|D@XO]
