OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FSue Roberts, whose brother Graham was
OL,8,Funlawfully killed at Hillsborough,
OL,9,Fdescribed the Bill's introduction as
OL,10,F"a huge step in the right direction"
OL,11,Fbut said the families will be
OL,12,F"watching closely to ensure this Bill
OL,13,Fis passed in its entirety and enacted
OL,14,Fin full".
OL,16,FShe added: "The Government must resist
OL,17,Fany pressure from those who don't
OL,18,Fbelieve the public deserves to know
OL,19,Fthe truth about when the state fails."
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@dO]tD@AOUvD@HO]xD@LOU{D@fO]
