OL,7,FAmong what the Government has
OL,8,Fdescribed as the "seismic changes" as
OL,9,Fpart of the Bill are the biggest
OL,10,Fexpansion of legal aid in a decade for
OL,11,Fbereaved families, with non-means
OL,12,Ftested help and support for inquests.
OL,14,FThis was welcomed by Julia Waters,
OL,15,Fsister of headteacher Ruth Perry who
OL,16,Ftook her own life after an Ofsted
OL,17,Freport downgraded her school.
OL,26,@pD@ROUpD@bO]
