OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FMs Waters said her family had been
OL,8,Fdenied legal aid for the inquest,
OL,9,Fmeaning they were "forced to crowdfund
OL,10,Fto cover our legal costs at an already
OL,11,Femotional and stressful time ` simply
OL,12,Fto be heard and to try to uncover the
OL,13,Ftruth", something she said felt
OL,14,F"profoundly unjust" when the public
OL,15,Fbodies involved had their legal costs
OL,16,Fcovered.
OL,26,@qD@SOUuD@FO]vD@AOUvD@SO]
