OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FThere will also be a new offence for
OL,8,Fmisleading the public, which the
OL,9,FGovernment said will mean criminal
OL,10,Fsanctions for the most serious
OL,11,Fbreaches.
OL,13,FNatasha Elcock, from Grenfell United,
OL,14,Fsaid: "It has been so easy for public
OL,15,Fand private agencies to escape
OL,16,Faccountability and scrutiny. By
OL,17,Festablishing a duty of candour,
OL,18,FHillsborough Law will prevent this,
OL,19,Fhelp us learn from failures and ensure
OL,20,Fbereaved and survivors are properly
OL,21,Fsupported."
OL,26,@vD@GOU}D@KO]
