OL,7,FLobby Akinnola, who lost his father,
OL,8,FFemi, early on in the Covid pandemic,
OL,9,Fsaid he and others had seen "first-
OL,10,Fhand how easily the truth is delayed,
OL,11,Fdiluted or denied", adding that this
OL,12,Fnew Bill is "a huge step towards"
OL,13,Fjustice.
